CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: TH International Limited is a company mainly engaged in the development and operation of coffee, donut, and tea restaurants in mainland China, operating under the brand name Tim Hortons. The Company offers freshly brewed coffee, tea and other beverages, breads and side dishes, and sandwiches. The Company also offers digital ordering, including delivery and self-pickup mobile ordering. The Company's restaurant chain includes company-owned and franchise locations.
